review_title: Didn't expect to love these sunglasses as much as I do!
reviews: I seem to constantly break and/or misplace my sunglasses so it's important that I don't pay an arm and a leg for them. These were super affordable, and I ended up loving them so much more than I ever thought I would. There's something about the tint (I chose the blue pair, I'm not sure if the tint is different based on which colour you get) that just makes everything look so incredibly vibrant and summery. I get complimented on them all the time, it's so strange because they're so simple! And LIGHT! I can barely feel them on my face - compared to some of the other sunglasses I have, they feel like I'm not even wearing glasses of any kind! I would definitely recommend these! I would recommend the wider version unless you have a very, very small head...I tried both sizes (I think I have a pretty average sized head) and the wider version was much more comfortable.
product_name: CGID E01 Retro Vintage John Lennon Inspired Round Metal Circle Polarized Sunglasses With Leather Case

reviews:
Absolutely fantastic glasses! Going to get a pair in the same style with prescription, so consider this a trial for style. Unlike my other pair of CGID, these actually came with a case, sleeve, and cleaning cloth. The lenses are truly polarized and are as described.

PROs:
- mirror finish... but you knew that already.
- spring hinge design
- no noticeable flashing or fusing residue on bridge or hinges
- polarized
- "value pack" with the case, sleeve and cloth

CONs:
- tint is brown... it doesn't specify but I'd rather have gray
- bridge wider than I'd like but this is the style

OVERALL:
- know the style you're buying into and there won't be any issues.
- just a small step under designer types but leagues ahead of drugstore or "fashion jewelry" glasses
product_name: CGID E01 Retro Vintage John Lennon Inspired Round Metal Circle Polarized Sunglasses With Leather Case

reviews:
I was scared when I purchased these sunglasses because I have a large head and I read some reviews by people who said they were too small. For reference I wear a size 8 hat and the circumference of my head is 64cm... I've got a large head. The glasses fit better than any pair of glasses I have ever owned. DO NOT buy the 47mm variety if you have a large head 51 is the way to go.

That being said... to be honest this is the first pair of sunglasses I have ever purchased that wasn't $5 or $10 at a drugstore... they're absolutely amazing... they're great at reducing glare... it makes the surface of the water look like a CGI or something. Would wholly recommend these glasses and I fully intend on purchasing another pair.

Best of all about these glasses... someone matched me on Tinder just to say they liked my glasses before unmatching me.
product_name: CGID E01 Retro Vintage John Lennon Inspired Round Metal Circle Polarized Sunglasses With Leather Case

review_title: Not metal, no anti-glare, Not Safe For Driving.
reviews:
They look decent enough, but they are cheap plastic frames, they have no anti-glare coating, but they deliver a few of the things they promise. Here are the promises they make:
Round - Yes
Metal - No
Circle - Uh, yes
Polarized - Yes
Sunglasses - No
Leather Case - Yes

You might ask why I said sunglasses as no when they are covered with a coating to darken. Well, without the anti-glare coating on them, they are basically useless. As someone who sold glasses, they amount of glare you get off your face from these glasses will render them completely unsafe for use outside for driving or doing anything important. DO NOT. USE THEM. FOR DRIVING.

review_title: Glasses have a weird and distracting glare!
reviews:

I received these glasses on time on December 12, 2018. However, due to a surgery, I wasn't able to test them well until recently. I very quickly noticed a weird glare when looking at bright surfaces and screens (my phone being my main concern as I plan to use these glasses outside and take photos while wearing them). I think this defeats the purpose of wearing sunglasses to help you see better when it gives off a peculiar and very distracting rainbow-ish glare when looking at bright surfaces/screens.

I am hoping to return or exchange these but I'm afraid that because I've passed the return window (Jan 31), I won't receive any compensation or help. Good looking glasses, but not effective.

Since her collection of these types of glasses has been growing gradually since then, I bought her these so that she could continue to strut her stuff in style. While these glasses are cool and seemed to be of a good quality, the problem is the lenses are very reflective‚Äìbasically blue-tined mirrors. While that may work for some, it was a bit much for Bahama Mama. As a result, we had to return them. Too bad the ad didn't state this clearly; I would never have ordered it in the first place.

review_title: Doesn't slip down when pulled up over your ears, 100% Polyester & machine washable.
reviews: Looking for something to wear to work, my wife settled on this super soft turtle neck type neck warmer. It came quickly and was exactly as described on Amazon. She has been using it for about a week now, and reports that it is really perfect for the cool to cold fall mornings to keep her ears and neck warm. It's stretchable, and well put together. The stitching is of a good quality, and there are is one seam on the back that is flat and smooth - not irritating. It's stretchable, more so width wise than length wise, and doesn't slip down when pulled up over your ears. 100% Polyester, and machine washable.

product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: beanie hat is fine/just as shown/i got the burgundy. It fits snug & my head is 21" around. fabric is like a thicker like a long john waffle type material. not really thin enough to be considered a summer hat maybe spring/fall. not bad though. take good care all.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: When I first tried this hat on, I thought there was no way I could make it fit. It seemed wayyy too big. But, with a little playing I managed to get it set on my head in a way that it stays on and looks pretty good (imo haha). I am a petite female so this hat fits me a bit on the large size. If I didn‚Äôt think it‚Äôd ruin it I‚Äôd try throwing it in the dryer to shrink it. But, I wear it all the time and love it. I love the color and it‚Äôs perfect for Spring and Fall.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: Very nice hat. Long in the back. I agree with other reviewers that this won't be useful for really cold temperatures because it's not made of warm fabrics. Good for the fall and spring. I have a larger head (about 22 in) which is the lower end of the size fit noted by the seller and this hat just fits, so I wouldn't recommend anyone with a smaller head ordering one.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: I needed something to keep my head warm for the sub zero weather. I'm not a fan of tight beanies and prefer the comfort of a loose (slouchy) beanie that can keep my head warm AND give my scalp some air. Hence this beanie. It came promptly and was just in time for my toboganning trip. It fit my head well and felt decently comfortable on my scalp. Unfortunately, after one wear, I lost it in the snow so I can't attest to the longevity of this product. However, it did well during my few hours of testing and I'll probably buy another one for next year.

reviews: Shipping was fast. I've had this for over a year, I wear it a lot and it's still in perfect condition. This is my favourite beanie to wear. I love how i slouches, it's really comfy (not too tight and not super baggy) and the colour is great.

reviews: When I first tried this hat on, I thought there was no way I could make it fit. It seemed wayyy too big. If I didn‚Äôt think it‚Äôd ruin it I‚Äôd try throwing it in the dryer to shrink it. But, I wear it all the time and love it. I love the color and it‚Äôs perfect for Spring and Fall.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: Very nice hat. Long in the back. I agree with other reviewers that this won't be useful for really cold temperatures because it's not made of warm fabrics. Good for the fall and spring. I have a larger head (about 22 in) which is the lower end of the size fit noted by the seller and this hat just fits, so I wouldn't recommend anyone with a smaller head ordering one.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: I needed something to keep my head warm for the sub zero weather. I'm not a fan of tight beanies and prefer the comfort of a loose (slouchy) beanie that can keep my head warm AND give my scalp some air. Hence this beanie. It came promptly and was just in time for my toboganning trip. It fit my head well and felt decently comfortable on my scalp. Unfortunately, after one wear, I lost it in the snow so I can't attest to the longevity of this product. However, it did well during my few hours of testing and I'll probably buy another one for next year.

product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: beanie hat is fine/just as shown/i got the burgundy. It fits snug & my head is 21" around. fabric is like a thicker like a long john waffle type material. not really thin enough to be considered a summer hat maybe spring/fall. not bad though. take good care all.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: When I first tried this hat on, I thought there was no way I could make it fit. It seemed wayyy too big. But, with a little playing I managed to get it set on my head in a way that it stays on and looks pretty good (imo haha). I am a petite female so this hat fits me a bit on the large size. If I didn‚Äôt think it‚Äôd ruin it I‚Äôd try throwing it in the dryer to shrink it. But, I wear it all the time and love it. I love the color and it‚Äôs perfect for Spring and Fall.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: Very nice hat. Long in the back. I agree with other reviewers that this won't be useful for really cold temperatures because it's not made of warm fabrics. Good for the fall and spring. I have a larger head (about 22 in) which is the lower end of the size fit noted by the seller and this hat just fits, so I wouldn't recommend anyone with a smaller head ordering one.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: I needed something to keep my head warm for the sub zero weather. I'm not a fan of tight beanies and prefer the comfort of a loose (slouchy) beanie that can keep my head warm AND give my scalp some air. Hence this beanie. It came promptly and was just in time for my toboganning trip. It fit my head well and felt decently comfortable on my scalp. Unfortunately, after one wear, I lost it in the snow so I can't attest to the longevity of this product. However, it did well during my few hours of testing and I'll probably buy another one for next year.

reviews: Shipping was fast. I've had this for over a year, I wear it a lot and it's still in perfect condition. This is my favourite beanie to wear. I love how i slouches, it's really comfy (not too tight and not super baggy) and the colour is great.

reviews: When I first tried this hat on, I thought there was no way I could make it fit. It seemed wayyy too big. If I didn‚Äôt think it‚Äôd ruin it I‚Äôd try throwing it in the dryer to shrink it. But, I wear it all the time and love it. I love the color and it‚Äôs perfect for Spring and Fall.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: Very nice hat. Long in the back. I agree with other reviewers that this won't be useful for really cold temperatures because it's not made of warm fabrics. Good for the fall and spring. I have a larger head (about 22 in) which is the lower end of the size fit noted by the seller and this hat just fits, so I wouldn't recommend anyone with a smaller head ordering one.
product_name: HISSHE Oversize Baggy Slouch Beanie Large Slouchy Skullcap Winter Summer Hat

reviews: I needed something to keep my head warm for the sub zero weather. I'm not a fan of tight beanies and prefer the comfort of a loose (slouchy) beanie that can keep my head warm AND give my scalp some air. Hence this beanie. It came promptly and was just in time for my toboganning trip. It fit my head well and felt decently comfortable on my scalp. Unfortunately, after one wear, I lost it in the snow so I can't attest to the longevity of this product. However, it did well during my few hours of testing and I'll probably buy another one for next year.
